{"tid":1541004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」下一次行動絕對要和理非","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T00:29:54.000Z","uid":82707,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2fccaa023329e823649a0af5c71e7293459b58b","tid":1541004,"uid":82707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:15:21.000Z","msg":"大家記得69 一百萬人遊行，非常和平理性<br />\n但正苦堅持唔肯撤回法案，先會導致612示威<br />\n由612開始，香港示威者都被國際標榜「民主鬥士」<br />\n我地之所以可以得到國際既同情同認同係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為「出師有名」！</span></span><br />\n每次大家夢遊國際都一致批評警察濫權，同情示威者<br />\n美國都因為同情香港人而將香港人權問題帶入中美貿易戰<br />\n我明白大家聽完林鄭撤回惡法感覺不安，但暫時真係唔好輕舉妄動！<br />\n林鄭撤惡法肯定唔係釋出善意，而係準備下一步更大既惡法-「緊急法」<br />\n如果我地貿然勇武，就畀正苦藉口用緊急法清洗太平地<br />\n可能大家覺得可以加速攬炒，但係依家情況比之前唔同，美國正式介入香港事務，好多美國議員承諾推行「人權法」<br />\n我地依家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有贏既籌碼</span></span>，唔再係孤兒仔<br />\n大家要趁依個機會展示香港人絕不妥協既決心，再搞多次二百萬人和理非遊行<br />\n記僅！法國黃衫軍失敗係因為馬克龍做咗所謂既「讓步」，而黃衫軍未有對應既準備就質然繼續勇武，令到好多原本支持佢地既法國人同國際都唔再支持佢地<br />\n<br />\n加上依家啲狗睇通哂前線既做法，由831開始晚晚有至少30個手足被捕<br />\n圍狗屋/ 快閃/ 陣地戰畀狗捉哂路<br />\n再加上黨鐵隨時封站同運兵既加持，勇武手足既成本太高<br />\n大家暫時停勇武唔係要大家唔再勇武，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而係要諗吓更有效既方法先再勇武</span></span><br />\n如果晚晚損失幾廿個兄弟，前線好快無人<br />\n<br />\n今次大家兵行危著，可以講係成個運動全危險既時候，希望前線暫停勇武，不宜係短時間勇武<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下次既行動要絕對和理非，畀世界知我地既五大訴求係未被接受！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0c2b1938499ca99e021a0c8c95b4d884dc5f24da","tid":1541004,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"233362b414501e160e88caa190645faecd69c97f","tid":1541004,"uid":82707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de610704c41874972eed6c119168fc81ff1177b","tid":1541004,"uid":283164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c60141ed6a73db69dd0343e0f2f655adebe791","tid":1541004,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n其實機場同美領都唔太適合勇武<br />\n機場要睇實際情況但應該有條件做到"},{"pid":"f626a55344836480da8bcd7908b60fb6934927bd","tid":1541004,"uid":82707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d3d4000196a53c881de2d7322d4dce5eafd176","tid":1541004,"uid":82707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fb7a580395a65d7fc590ac3387cdb8afff1c71","tid":1541004,"uid":82707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25d2463bc7d7f525b95a98aba02209f6b9504a3","tid":1541004,"uid":82707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f33367f39d9fdc650f6a6554d20801488035261","tid":1541004,"uid":82707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b61fa56df25a407aeabbeb9a4d40e9bddfe587","tid":1541004,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:40:05.000Z","msg":"一齊打經濟戰<br />\n抵制藍絲餐廳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kA